docs.lead_paragraph: LONDON, Feb. 10--Taking the protective measures usual in times of crisis and uncertainty, such as the industrial shutdown now in effect, jobbers marked down share prices substantially in the stock markets today. When it was seen, however, that little actual selling was taking place many of the leaders finished the day above the lowest levels.
